text: I Am is the fifth studio album by British recording artist Leona Lewis. It was released on 11 September 2015, by Island Records after Lewis left Syco Music in June 2014, she had been with that label ever since she had won The X Factor in 2006. ==Track listing== denotes co-producer ==Charts== Chart (2015) Peak position Australian Albums (ARIA) 82 == Release history == List of release dates, showing country, format, label, edition, and reference Country Date Edition Format Label Ireland 11 September 2015 Island United Kingdom United States Def Jam ==References== Category:2015 albums Category:Leona Lewis albums Category:R&B; albums
